data.description: Welcome home to this 3 bedroom/ 3 bath ranch home tucked away on 2.95  private acres located near the heart of Covington. This large ranch features built in can lights with speakers in the  living area, breakfast area in the kitchen with a view to the secluded back yard, two owner suites and a third bedroom with built in desk that is perfect for a student or working from home. Enjoy a quiet evening on the front porch or reading a book on the screened back porch. The huge basement has a workshop area, private entrances to the basement and plenty of room to make an in law suite, teen suite or man cave. There is even a pool table in place that is negotiable with the right offer.  Come take a look at this gem that is in a perfect location if you are looking for that quiet country feel but close to shopping, restaurants, movie studios, the interstate and the famous Covington Square.
